{"root":{"data":{"id":"d22s82zdxmo0","created":1718677211226,"text":"第八章 工业控制系统的数据通信"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22s8p3hew00","created":1718677259363,"text":"网络标准"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22s8sw89gw0","created":1718677267632,"text":"通信网络的特点"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22s8x19k1k0","created":1718677276643,"text":"❖ 实时性好，动态响应快；"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22s8x19fns0","created":1718677276643,"text":"❖ 可靠性高；"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22s8x19dq00","created":1718677276643,"text":"❖ 适应恶劣的工业现场环境；"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22s8x191p40","created":1718677276643,"text":"❖ 开放系统互连和互操作性。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d22s93m9ets0","created":1718677290974,"text":"OSI参考模型"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22s9ba75080","created":1718677307659,"text":"协议："},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d22s9gjsfx40","created":1718677319122,"text":"1）包括数据格式、信号电平等规定；"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22s9gjs7iw0","created":1718677319122,"text":"2）包括用于调整和差错处理的控制信息；"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22s9gjsf4w0","created":1718677319122,"text":"3）时序，包括速度匹配和排序"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d22s9tee4mg0","created":1718677347094,"text":"各层所共有的功能："},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22s9tee05c0","created":1718677347094,"text":"1）封装过程；使高一层的数据不包含低层的控制信息。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22s9teeus80","created":1718677347095,"text":"2）分段存储；对信息的分组、传送、重组进行通信。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22s9teeoio0","created":1718677347095,"text":"3）连接建立；数据报和虚连接。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22s9teei0o0","created":1718677347095,"text":"4）流量控制；保证不发生数据溢出。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22s9teeni80","created":1718677347095,"text":"5）差错控制；以检测和纠正产生差错的机制。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d22s9teeq540","created":1718677347095,"text":"6）多路复用；改善可靠性、性能或者效率。"},"children":[]}]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}